Test::Signature

   Test::Signature verifies that the Module::Signature generated
   signature of a module is correct.

For installation details, see INSTALL.

For usage, see the doco. Either use perldoc or view it
on the web at:
    <http://search.cpan.org/author/SPOON/Test-Signature/>

Changes for 1.03 (29 Oct 2002)
   - Updated recommended version of Module::Signature
   - Checks for network availability. As taken from MS 0.16

For a complete list of changes, see the Changes file.


by Iain Truskett.
